Package com.heretere.hdl.dependency.maven

Class MavenDependencyInfo

java.lang.Object
com.heretere.hdl.dependency.maven.MavenDependencyInfo
All Implemented Interfaces:
Dependency, RelocatableDependency
public final class MavenDependencyInfo
extends Object
implements RelocatableDependency
This is the backend class for MavenDependency dependencies. It's responsible for providing basic information needed to download and relocate a dependency jar.
See Also:
MavenDependency
